{
  "id": "adv_main_01_08_06",
  "title": "星見編2章11話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-3d",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "…………げ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Agh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.566666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 199.99999999999974,
          "startTime": 2.7666666666666666
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんですか？\nスマホ見ながら、急に変な声出して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's wrong?\nYou just made a weird sound while looking at your phone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.733333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.839347612552155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ううん……な、なんでもないんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ um… i-it’s nothing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.972680945885488,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9133.333333333338,
          "startTime": 19.106014279218826
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "ごめん、ちょっとだけ電話してくるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ I’ve gotta make a quick phone call.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.539347612552156,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "なんか、気になりますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Curious indeed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.972680945885497,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 43.33333333330458,
          "startTime": 20.0160142792188
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 33.333333333327886,
          "startTime": 20.006014279218824
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 466.66666666666146,
          "startTime": 20.439347612552158
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "……事件の、予感？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "….The premonition of an event?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.972680945885497,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……二人とも、そのやりとり好きだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You two seem to be enjoying this a little too much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.599143643868288,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんのあんな苦々しい顔……\n初めて見たかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t think I’ve ever seen\nHaruko-san looking so distressed before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.317805842252895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "なにかよっぽど面倒な連絡、でもあったのかな？\nちょっと気になる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder if she received some troublesome news.\nI’m a little curious…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.31780584225288,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、見て\n遙子ちゃん、扉のすぐ外で電話してるみたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "….Oh‚ look!\nShe’s making a call right outside the door.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.81780584225288,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "聞き耳……チャンス",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our chance… to eavesdrop.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.61780584225288,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1000,
          "startTime": 47.61780584225288
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1399.9999999999914,
          "startTime": 48.01780584225287
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "も、もう二人とも……気になるのはわかるけど\n盗み聞きなんて、その……よ、よくないよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-you guys… I get that you’re curious‚\nbut eavesdropping is‚ you know… n-not good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.19755638012519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "ほんとよ。そんな不審者みたいなことしなくても\n戻ってきてから聞いてみたらいいじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It really isn’t. Instead of doing something so shady‚\nwe can just ask her when she gets back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.53088971345852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_plan-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 68.63088971345847
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……と言いつつ、俺たちみんな\n結局こうして聞き耳を立てちゃってるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…If that’s the case‚ why are all of us\ntrying to pick up on what she’s saying?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.2308897134585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}さん、しーっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ shhh!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.39755638012517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに……続け……じゃ無理よ\nそういう……だもん……嫌ってわけ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no way… not while continuing as…\nThat’s my… It’s not that I don’t want…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.13179668952253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "だから……そう勝手に……できない\nもう！ ……考えて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like I said… always deciding for me… I can’t do it.\nJeez… Try and think about…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.09846335618928,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……やっぱりドア越しだとよく聞こえないね\nなにか断ってるみたいだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… Can’t seem to hear very well from this side of the door.\nIt sounds like she’s turning something down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.79846335618927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして……\n壺でも売りつけられてるとか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could it be…\nSomeone’s trying to scam her into buying antiques?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.4984633561892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そんなバカな……仮にそうだとしても\n遙子さんならちゃんと断れるだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no way… Even if that were the case‚\nHaruko-san should be more than capable of saying no.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.7317966895226,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あの、でも……遙子さんこの前\n訪問販売の人と、玄関でずっと話し込んでて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ um‚ but… the other day‚ Haruko-san spent forever\ntalking to a salesperson at the dorm entrance……and",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.4651300228559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "化粧品、買わされそうに、なってた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "almost ended up buying a bunch of cosmetics.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.73179668952255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "……あっ。こっちに来ちゃう！\nみんな戻って戻って！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh! Here she comes!\nEveryone‚ back‚ back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.0890530384505,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2500,
          "startTime": 132.65571970511704
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2866.666666666845,
          "startTime": 133.02238637178388
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……まったくもう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh* Unbelievable…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.8557197051172,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 33.33333333335986,
          "startTime": 133.88905303845056
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "お……お帰り、遙子さん\nなんの電話だったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wel… welcome back‚ Haruko-san.\nWhat was the call about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.4557198004844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……えっと……\n大した用事じゃなかったんだけど……って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… er…\nNothing important‚ but… Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.8557198004843,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_06-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたの、みんな？\nなんだか、よそよそしいけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s the matter‚ guys?\nYou’re all acting strangely distant.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.7557198004844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
